{"id":143,"parent_id":110,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":143,"title":"Alma 33","subtitle":"","short_title":"Alma","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 33"],[".studySummary",["i","Zenos taught that men should pray and worship in all places, and that judgments are turned away because of the Son—Zenock taught that mercy is bestowed because of the Son—Moses had lifted up in the wilderness a type of the Son of God. About 74",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.1","order":"05.20.033.15598"},["b","1"],"Now after Alma had spoken these words, they sent forth unto him desiring to know whether they should believe in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"one God"],", that they might obtain this fruit of which he had spoken, or",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"how"],"they should plant the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"seed"],", or the word of which he had spoken, which he said must be planted in their hearts; or in what manner they should begin to exercise their faith."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.2","order":"05.20.033.15599"},["b","2"],"And Alma said unto them: Behold, ye have said that ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"could"],"not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"worship"],"your God because ye are cast out of your synagogues. But behold, I say unto you, if ye suppose that ye cannot worship God, ye do greatly err, and ye ought to search the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"scriptures"],"; if ye suppose that they have taught you this, ye do not understand them."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.3","order":"05.20.033.15600"},["b","3"],"Do ye remember to have read what",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Zenos"],", the prophet of old, has said concerning prayer or",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"worship"],"?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.4","order":"05.20.033.15601"},["b","4"],"For he said: Thou art merciful, O God, for thou hast heard my prayer, even when I was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"in"],"the wilderness; yea, thou wast merciful when I prayed concerning those who were mine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"enemies"],", and thou didst turn them to me."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.5","order":"05.20.033.15602"},["b","5"],"Yea, O God, and thou wast merciful unto me when I did cry unto thee in my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"field"],"; when I did cry unto thee in my prayer, and thou didst hear me."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.6","order":"05.20.033.15603"},["b","6"],"And again, O God, when I did turn to my house thou didst hear me in my prayer."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.7","order":"05.20.033.15604"},["b","7"],"And when I did turn unto my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"closet"],", O Lord, and prayed unto thee, thou didst hear me."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.8","order":"05.20.033.15605"},["b","8"],"Yea, thou art merciful unto thy children when they cry unto thee, to be heard of thee and not of men, and thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"wilt hear"],"them."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.9","order":"05.20.033.15606"},["b","9"],"Yea, O God, thou hast been merciful unto me, and heard my cries in the midst of thy congregations."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.10","order":"05.20.033.15607"},["b","10"],"Yea, and thou hast also heard me when I have been",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"cast out"],"and have been despised by mine enemies; yea, thou didst hear my cries, and wast angry with mine enemies, and thou didst",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"visit"],"them in thine anger with speedy destruction."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.11","order":"05.20.033.15608"},["b","11"],"And thou didst hear me because of mine afflictions and my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"sincerity"],"; and it is because of thy Son that thou hast been thus merciful unto me, therefore I will cry unto thee in all mine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"afflictions"],", for in thee is my joy; for thou hast turned thy judgments away from me,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"because"],"of thy Son."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.12","order":"05.20.033.15609"},["b","12"],"And now Alma said unto them: Do ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"believe"],"those scriptures which have been written by them of old?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.13","order":"05.20.033.15610"},["b","13"],"Behold, if ye do, ye must believe what",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Zenos"],"said; for, behold he said: Thou hast turned away thy judgments because of thy Son."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.14","order":"05.20.033.15611"},["b","14"],"Now behold, my brethren, I would ask if ye have read the scriptures? If ye have, how can ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"disbelieve"],"on the Son of God?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.15","order":"05.20.033.15612"},["b","15"],"For it is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"not"],"written that Zenos alone spake of these things, but",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"Zenock"],"also spake of these things—"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.16","order":"05.20.033.15613"},["b","16"],"For behold, he said: Thou art angry, O Lord, with this people, because they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"will"],"not understand thy mercies which thou hast bestowed upon them because of thy Son."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.17","order":"05.20.033.15614"},["b","17"],"And now, my brethren, ye see that a second prophet of old has testified of the Son of God, and because the people would not understand his words they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"stoned"],"him to death."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.18","order":"05.20.033.15615"},["b","18"],"But behold, this is not all; these are not the only ones who have spoken concerning the Son of God."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.19","order":"05.20.033.15616"},["b","19"],"Behold, he was spoken of by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Moses"],"; yea, and behold a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"type"],"was",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"raised"],"up in the wilderness, that whosoever would look upon it might live. And many did look and live."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.20","order":"05.20.033.15617"},["b","20"],"But few understood the meaning of those things, and this because of the hardness of their hearts. But there were many who were so hardened that they would not look, therefore they perished. Now the reason they would not look is because they did not believe that it would",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"heal"],"them."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.21","order":"05.20.033.15618"},["b","21"],"O my brethren, if ye could be healed by merely casting about your eyes that ye might be healed, would ye not behold quickly, or would ye rather harden your hearts in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"unbelief"],", and be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"slothful"],", that ye would not cast about your eyes, that ye might perish?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.22","order":"05.20.033.15619"},["b","22"],"If so, wo shall come upon you; but if not so, then cast about your eyes and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"begin"],"to believe in the Son of God, that he will come to redeem his people, and that he shall suffer and die to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"atone"],"for their sins; and that he shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"rise"],"again from the dead, which shall bring to pass the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_22d"},"resurrection"],", that all men shall stand before him, to be",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_22e"},"judged"],"at the last and judgment day, according to their",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_22f"},"works"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.23","order":"05.20.033.15620"},["b","23"],"And now, my brethren, I desire that ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"plant"],"this word in your hearts, and as it beginneth to swell even so nourish it by your faith. And behold, it will become a tree,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"springing up"],"in you unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"everlasting life"],". And then may God grant unto you that your",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_23d"},"burdens"],"may be light, through the joy of his Son. And even all this can ye do if ye",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_23e"},"will"],". Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.1a","order":"05.20.033.15621"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.21"},"2 Ne. 31:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.4"},"Mosiah 15:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.28.28-35"},"Alma 11:28 (28–35)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.1b","order":"05.20.033.15623"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.23"},"Alma 33:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.1c","order":"05.20.033.15625"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.28.28-43"},"Alma 32:28 (28–43)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.2a","order":"05.20.033.15627"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.5"},"Alma 32:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.2b","order":"05.20.033.15629"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worship"},"TG Worship"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.2c","order":"05.20.033.15631"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.34"},"Mosiah 2:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.8.3-10"},"Alma 37:8 (3–10)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"TG Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.3a","order":"05.20.033.15633"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.7"},"Alma 34:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-lost"},"TG Scriptures, Lost"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.3b","order":"05.20.033.15635"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worship"},"TG Worship"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.4a","order":"05.20.033.15637"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.47.44-52"},"1 Kgs. 8:47 (44–52)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.4b","order":"05.20.033.15639"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.44"},"Matt. 5:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.5a","order":"05.20.033.15641"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.20.20-25"},"Alma 34:20 (20–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.7a","order":"05.20.033.15643"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/6.6.5-6"},"Matt. 6:6 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.26.17-27"},"Alma 34:26 (17–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.8a","order":"05.20.033.15645"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-access-to"},"TG God, Access to"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.10a","order":"05.20.033.15647"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.5"},"Alma 32:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.10b","order":"05.20.033.15649"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/3.7"},"Ps. 3:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.17"},"18:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.11a","order":"05.20.033.15651"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sincere"},"TG Sincere"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.11b","order":"05.20.033.15653"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/affliction"},"TG Affliction"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.11c","order":"05.20.033.15655"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.12a","order":"05.20.033.15657"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-value-of"},"TG Scriptures, Value of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.13a","order":"05.20.033.15659"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.1"},"Jacob 6:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.7"},"Alma 34:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.14a","order":"05.20.033.15661"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.39"},"John 5:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.15a","order":"05.20.033.15663"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.4"},"Jacob 4:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.11.11-13"},"Mosiah 15:11 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.15b","order":"05.20.033.15665"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.10"},"1 Ne. 19:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.7"},"Alma 34:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.16a","order":"05.20.033.15667"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.5.4-5"},"2 Pet. 3:5 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.17a","order":"05.20.033.15669"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.19a","order":"05.20.033.15671"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/18.15.15,18"},"Deut. 18:15 (15, 18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.7"},"Alma 34:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.19b","order":"05.20.033.15673"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/21.9"},"Num. 21:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.41"},"1 Ne. 17:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.20"},"2 Ne. 25:20"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/symbolism"},"Symbolism"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.19c","order":"05.20.033.15675"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/3.14"},"John 3:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/8.14"},"Hel. 8:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.20a","order":"05.20.033.15677"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/11.3"},"Hosea 11:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.41.40-41"},"1 Ne. 17:41 (40–41)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.21a","order":"05.20.033.15679"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/doubt"},"TG Doubt"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.21b","order":"05.20.033.15681"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apathy"},"TG Apathy"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/laziness"},"Laziness"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.22a","order":"05.20.033.15683"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.16"},"Alma 25:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.46.45-46"},"37:46 (45–46)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.22b","order":"05.20.033.15685"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.10"},"2 Ne. 2:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/22.14"},"Alma 22:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.9.8-16"},"34:9 (8–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.22c","order":"05.20.033.15687"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"22d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.22d","order":"05.20.033.15689"},["b","22d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.44"},"Alma 11:44"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"22e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.22e","order":"05.20.033.15691"},["b","22e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"22f","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.22f","order":"05.20.033.15693"},["b","22f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.23a","order":"05.20.033.15695"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.1"},"Alma 33:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.4"},"34:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.23b","order":"05.20.033.15697"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.41"},"Alma 32:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.23"},"D&C 63:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.23c","order":"05.20.033.15699"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.43"},"Alma 32:43"],"."],["div",{"id":"23d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.23d","order":"05.20.033.15701"},["b","23d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/24.15.13-15"},"Mosiah 24:15 (13–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/31.38"},"Alma 31:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"23e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.23e","order":"05.20.033.15703"},["b","23e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/agency"},"TG Agency"],"."]]}
